{
  "stem": "24111.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the road, the-- the partisans closed by cutting down all the trees.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the trees were laying over the road.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That way, they prevented their-- the Italian cars coming up certain roads.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They made barriers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We walked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had one of their horse-drawn carriages for our, you know belongings.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went to Ljubljana.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were put on one railroad car.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were hooked up to the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the train went from Ljubljana, to Postumia Grotte, to Trieste, and from Trieste up Bologna to Modena.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And an interesting thing is that the Germans knew about our group, too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they requested the Italian government, the Italian local government, when they requested the-- the-- the-- the wagon, the railway car, for us, to send the car, instead of Trieste, Bologna, Modena, to Trevizo and up to Germany.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And their-- their request was actually denied by the Italian government.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we arrived in Modena, after I think a day or day and a half long journey, the Modena-- the Modena Jewish community-- they have a beautiful temple there-- took us in-- in-- into their temple and provided food and shelter for the children, who were exhausted at that time.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I forgot to tell you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Joschko and our group of 10 adults, I should say-- Joschko was the main-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and he, perhaps, was the brain of the group.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, he was the-- the-- the direct-- giving the directions.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we always had contact with the outside world.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this is an amazing fact.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were in contact in-- when we were in Lesno Brdo, in '41 and '42, with Switzerland, with the the only shaliach in whole Europe, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in-- in Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
